{"id":"df2e0f6c-70a9-4eaf-920a-15d7a10858f2","name":"Emma Grace Frost","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">“Don’t gloat, child. It’s a sign of poor upbringing.”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_15201dbb-0ffe-4f5e-8c98-2b519780b76f.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 339px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">“Of course <span style=\"color: rgb(112, 228, 236)\">I'm a threat</span>. Why? Did you think for a moment that I wasn't?”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_cd8746a9-9f27-4a44-b685-e5aebff181ec.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\">Emma Grace Frost </span>is a powerful and influential <span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\">mutant</span> telepath, most notoriously known as the <span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\"><strong>White Queen</strong></span> of the <span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\"><strong>Hellfire Club</strong></span> and occasional headmistress of the <span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\">Xavier's School for Gifted Youngsters</span>. Born to a rich Boston mercantile family, she parted ways with her family and built a financial empire with <span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\">Frost International</span>, ascending to a ruling position in the Inner <span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\">Circle of the Hellfire Club.</span> Demonstrating a particular interest in education, Frost ran the Massachusetts Academy, a preparatory school that secretly housed young mutants trained for her own interests, the <span style=\"color: rgb(160, 231, 245)\">Hellions</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_2549d228-ccd5-4d93-a574-ee1f663bd9ca.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 500px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">“Sowing seeds of <strong>distrust</strong> is all fine and dandy, Emma......but now it's time......to get......<strong>drastic</strong>.”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/54/1b/d2/541bd297e4bc9a43f5e9106589cda5b8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"object-fit: contain; width: 506px; margin: 0px auto;\" loading=\"auto\" class=\"hCL kVc L4E MIw N7A XiG\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_8f9dedad-35b5-4c6b-a937-4c6aaae176c3.webp","creator":"The TiredTimes","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦄 Non-human"],"chats":2797,"messages":40183,"created_at":"2025-01-20T18:20:42.706295+00:00"}